2 months ago I posted my first coffee tour video and little did I know it’d lead me to 23 different coffee shops in 19 different areas ☕️ I’ve met so many incredible people / small business owners along the way, and I can’t wait to keep it going. The coffee community is a special one. 

I’ve invested a lot into this series, so I really appreciate all the support. It motivates me and gives me confidence in my ability to create / tell a story. Never stop doing what you love ❤️
